enumerationMembers.label: ActiveActionStatus
enumerationMembers.comment: An in-progress action (e.g., while watching the movie, or driving to a location).

enumerationMembers.label: CompletedActionStatus
enumerationMembers.comment: An action that has already taken place.

enumerationMembers.label: FailedActionStatus
enumerationMembers.comment: An action that failed to complete. The action's error property and the HTTP return code contain more information about the failure.

enumerationMembers.label: PotentialActionStatus
enumerationMembers.comment: A description of an action that is supported.
